name: Museum Strasser Häusl
description:
The Strasser Häusl museum covers the expectional story of the Strasser children who made the Christmas carol 'Silent Night' famous to the world over with their concert performances.
With its characterful charm the Strasser Häusl also provides visitors with an impressive tour of the age-old rural culture of the Zillertal.

Opening times: closed during the winter season 2016/17
